## What's Changed
* feat: support for reading gzip, bzip2 and xz files by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/363
* feat: add `--show-mtime` (`-M`) option by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/350
* feat: add option `--no-unicode` to disable unicode symbols by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/362
* fix: division by zero error in formatFileRow by @xroberx in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/359

## New Contributors
* @xroberx made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/359

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/dundee/gdu/compare/v5.28.0...v5.29.0
